title: Dak Prescott, Nascar, Jamal Adams, MLB, Patriots
itunes:title: Dak Prescott, Nascar, Jamal Adams, MLB, Patriots
description:
Colin discusses Dak Prescott wanting a shorter deal, Nascar finally moving in the right direction, why Jamal Adams wants to be traded, the proposed 60 game MLB season, and why the Patriots won't make the playoffs. Guests include Danny Kanell, Jon Paul Morosi, Dan Fouts, and Stanford Routt.
